{"language": "html", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AX역량강화 Hub — 교육과정 & 인증 연계</title>
<style>
:root {
  --bg-primary: #ffffff;
  --bg-secondary: #f7f6f3;
  --bg-tertiary: #f0efe9;
  --text-primary: #1a1917;
  --text-secondary: #6b6963;
  --text-tertiary: #9c9a92;
  --border-tertiary: rgba(26,25,23,0.12);
  --border-secondary: rgba(26,25,23,0.22);
  --border-primary: rgba(26,25,23,0.38);
  --success: #1D9E75;
  --radius-md: 8px;
  --radius-lg: 12px;
}
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --bg-primary: #1c1b19;
    --bg-secondary: #242320;
    --bg-tertiary: #2c2b27;
    --text-primary: #e8e6df;
    --text-secondary: #a09e96;
    --text-tertiary: #6b6963;
    --border-tertiary: rgba(232,230,223,0.1);
    --border-secondary: rgba(232,230,223,0.18);
    --border-primary: rgba(232,230,223,0.3);
  }
}
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body {
  font-family: 'Pretendard', 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
  background: var(--bg-tertiary);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  min-height: 100vh;
  padding: 2rem 1rem;
}
.outer {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.page-header {
  margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  padding-bottom: 1.25rem;
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border-tertiary);
}
.page-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: .06em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  background: #fdecea;
  color: #b91c1c;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.page-title {
  font-size: 26px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  line-height: 1.2;
}
.page-sub {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.card {
  background: var(--bg-primary);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border-tertiary);
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.hub-tabs {
  display: flex;
  gap: 6px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.ht {
  padding: 5px 14px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border-secondary);
  background: transparent;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  transition: all .15s;
  font-family: inherit;
}
.ht.on {
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  border-color: var(--border-primary);
  background: var(--bg-secondary);
}
.ht:hover:not(.on) { background: var(--bg-secondary); }
.grid4 {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0,1fr));
  gap: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.lv-card {
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border-tertiary);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 12px 10px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all .15s;
  background: var(--bg-primary);
  text-align: center;
}
.lv-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-secondary); background: var(--bg-secondary); }
.lv-card.on { background: var(--bg-secondary); }
.lv-pill {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 2px 9px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.lv-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 3px; }
.lv-meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5; }
.dp {
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border-tertiary);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 16px;
  background: var(--bg-secondary);
}
.dp-badge { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px; white-space: nowrap; margin-bottom: 10px; display: inline-block; }
.dp-info { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 6px; }
.dp-tag { font-size: 11px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 20px; border: 0.5px solid var(--border-tertiary); background: var(--bg-primary); color: var(--text-secondary); }
.dp-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 5px; }
.dp-goal { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0,1fr) minmax(0,1fr); gap: 9px; margin-bottom: 9px; }
.col-box { border: 0.5px solid var(--border-tertiary); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 11px; background: var(--bg-primary); }
.col-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-tertiary); letter-spacing: .04em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.col-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.col-body { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.55; }
.outcome-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
.outcome-list li { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.55; padding: 3px 0 3px 16px; position: relative; }
.outcome-list li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #1D9E75; font-size: 11px; }
.chip { display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 20px; border: 0.5px solid var(--border-tertiary); background: var(--bg-primary); color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 2px 2px 0 0; }
.ab { margin-top: 10px; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: var(--radius-md); border: 0.5px solid var(--border-secondary); background: transparent; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); transition: all .15s; font-family: inherit; }
.ab:hover { background: var(--bg-secondary); color: var(--text-primary); }
.pnl { display: none; }
.pnl.on { display: block; }
.dvd { border: none; border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border-tertiary); margin: .85rem 0; }
.tl-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 8px; margin-top: 1rem; }
.tl-card { border: 0.5px solid var(--border-tertiary); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 11px; background: var(--bg-primary); }
.tl-m { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 5px; }
.tl-b { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.65; }
.kpi-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 8px; }
.kpi-c { background: var(--bg-secondary); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 11px; border: 0.5px solid var(--border-tertiary); }
.kpi-l { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-bottom: 3px; }
.kpi-v { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-primary); }
.kpi-u { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); }
.kpi-d { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-top: 3px; }
.track-bar { display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.tp { padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 20px; border: 0.5px solid var(--border-secondary); background: transparent; cursor: pointer; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); transition: all .15s; font-family: inherit; }
.tp.on { background: var(--bg-secondary); color: var(--text-primary); border-color: var(--border-primary); font-weight: 500; }
.prog-bar { height: 4px; border-radius: 2px; background: var(--border-tertiary); margin: 6px 0 10px; overflow: hidden; }
.prog-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 2px; background: #1D9E75; }
.sec-label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 8px; }
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .grid4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); }
  .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .tl-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); }
  .kpi-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0,1fr)); }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="outer">

  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-badge">AI Transformation 역량 체계</div>
    <div class="page-title">AX역량강화 Hub</div>
    <div class="page-sub">생성형 AI의 기본 활용부터 엔터프라이즈 Agent 거버넌스까지,<br>4단계 레벨 체계로 체계적인 AX 역량을 갖추세요.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="hub-tabs">
      <button class="ht on" onclick="sw('cert',this)">레벨별 교육과정</button>
      <button class="ht" onclick="sw('map',this)">인증 연계 매핑</button>
      <button class="ht" onclick="sw('track',this)">Track A / B</button>
      <button class="ht" onclick="sw('tl',this)">시행 타임라인</button>
      <button class="ht" onclick="sw('kpi',this)">KPI</button>
    </div>

    <!-- ══ TAB 1: 레벨별 교육과정 ══ -->
    <div id="pnl-cert" class="pnl on">
      <div class="grid4">
        <div class="lv-card on" id="lc1" onclick="sel(1)" style="border-color:#d94f3d;border-width:1.5px">
          <div class="lv-pill" style="background:#fdecea;color:#b91c1c">LEVEL 1</div>
          <div class="lv-name">AX Starter</div>
          <div class="lv-meta">약 150분 · 5모듈<br>10세션 · 전 구성원</div>
        </div>
        <div class="lv-card" id="lc2" onclick="sel(2)">
          <div class="lv-pill" style="background:#fff7e6;color:#b45309">LEVEL 2</div>
          <div class="lv-name">AX Advanced</div>
          <div class="lv-meta">약 185분 · 5모듈<br>9세션 · Lv.1 이수자</div>
        </div>
        <div class="lv-card" id="lc3" onclick="sel(3)">
          <div class="lv-pill" style="background:#EEEDFE;color:#534AB7">LEVEL 3</div>
          <div class="lv-name">AX Operator</div>
          <div class="lv-meta">약 245분 · 8모듈<br>19세션 · AI 기획자/파워유저</div>
        </div>
        <div class="lv-card" id="lc4" onclick="sel(4)">
          <div class="lv-pill" style="background:#E6F1FB;color:#185FA5">LEVEL 4</div>
          <div class="lv-name">AX Expert</div>
          <div class="lv-meta">약 265분 · 8모듈<br>18세션 · AI/ML 엔지니어</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dp" id="cert-dp">
        <div class="dp-badge" id="dp-badge" style="background:#fdecea;color:#b91c1c">LEVEL 1 — AX Starter</div>
        <div class="dp-info" style="margin-bottom:10px">
          <span class="dp-tag" id="dp-t1">약 150분</span>
          <span class="dp-tag" id="dp-t2">5개 모듈</span>
          <span class="dp-tag" id="dp-t3">10세션</span>
          <span class="dp-tag" id="dp-t4">전 구성원 (AI 도구 사용 경험 무관)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="dp-title" id="dp-title">AI Tool을 업무에 활용 가능한 역량</div>
        <div class="dp-goal" id="dp-goal">Generative AI(생성형 AI)의 작동 원리와 한계를 이해하고, 구조화된 Prompt(프롬프트)로 업무 산출물(요약/초안/정리)을 안전하게 생성할 수 있다</div>
        <div class="two-col">
          <div class="col-box">
            <div class="col-label">학습 후 모습</div>
            <ul class="outcome-list" id="dp-outcomes">
              <li>Role·Context·Format 포함 구조화된 Prompt 작성</li>
              <li>Hallucination 인지 및 AI 결과물 검증 습관 형성</li>
              <li>사내 보안·저작권 가이드라인 준수하여 AI 활용</li>
              <li>AI Agent 존재와 가능성 인지 및 상위 학습 방향성</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-box">
            <div class="col-label">역량인증 연계</div>
            <div id="dp-cert-info">
              <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text-primary);margin-bottom:5px">AX Starter 인증 (4월 오픈)</div>
              <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin-bottom:8px">교육 이수 + 온라인 과제 제출</div>
              <span class="chip">Track A 시작점</span>
              <span class="chip">DX Lv.1 → AX Lv.1 전환 가능</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-box" style="margin-bottom:0">
          <div class="col-label">주요 학습 키워드</div>
          <div id="dp-keywords">
            <span class="chip">GenAI 작동원리</span><span class="chip">구조화 Prompt</span><span class="chip">Role·Context·Format</span><span class="chip">Hallucination 검증</span><span class="chip">보안·저작권</span><span class="chip">AI Agent 개념</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ══ TAB 2: 인증 연계 매핑 ══ -->
    <div id="pnl-map" class="pnl">
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1fr) minmax(0,1fr);gap:9px">
        <div class="col-box" style="border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:14px">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px">
            <span class="lv-pill" style="background:#fdecea;color:#b91c1c;margin:0">Lv.1</span>
            <span style="font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text-primary)">AX Starter 연계</span>
          </div>
          <div class="col-title">인증 조건</div>
          <div class="col-body" style="margin-bottom:7px">교육 이수 + 온라인 과제 · 4월 오픈 · 전 구성원</div>
          <div class="col-title" style="margin-top:7px">교육 핵심 내용</div>
          <div class="col-body" style="margin-bottom:7px">GenAI 원리, 구조화 Prompt, Hallucination 검증, 보안 준수</div>
          <div class="col-title" style="margin-top:7px">연계 Hub 과정</div>
          <span class="chip">1일 AX 집중과정</span><span class="chip">MS Copilot 기초</span>
        </div>
        <div class="col-box" style="border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:14px">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px">
            <span class="lv-pill" style="background:#fff7e6;color:#b45309;margin:0">Lv.2</span>
            <span style="font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text-primary)">AX Advanced 연계</span>
          </div>
          <div class="col-title">인증 조건</div>
          <div class="col-body" style="margin-bottom:7px">교육 이수 + 업무 적용 포트폴리오 · 4월 오픈 · Lv.1 이수자</div>
          <div class="col-title" style="margin-top:7px">교육 핵심 내용</div>
